      "value": "<p>&gt;@Compendium[sfrpg.class-features.G7p2YIGFTAU6uGjL]{Stellar Revelation}</p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTalentsAll_ctl07_LabelName\" style=\"font-family: var(--font-primary); font-size: var(--font-size-14);\"><sub style=\"font-family: var(--font-primary);\"><img style=\"border: 1px solid var(--color-border-dark);\" src=\"systems/sfrpg/images/cup/gameplay/photon.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></sub><span style=\"font-family: var(--font-primary); font-size: var(--font-size-14);\">&nbsp;</span></span><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTalentsAll_ctl07_LabelName\">Photon Revelation</span><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTalentsAll_ctl07_LabelName\"><br /></span>As a move action, you can cause all of your melee attacks to deal fire damage instead of their normal damage type. (The attacks are still made against the target&rsquo;s EAC or KAC as normal for the weapon.) This benefit lasts for 1 round or until you leave photon mode.</p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTalentsAll_ctl13_LabelName\"><br />When you are attuned or fully attuned, your attacks with plasma sheath deal additional fire damage equal to half your level.</span></p>"
